# Changelog
All notable changes to this project will be documented in this file.

The format is based on [Keep a Changelog](https://keepachangelog.com/en/1.0.0/)
and this project adheres to [Semantic Versioning](https://semver.org/spec/v2.0.0.html).

## [Unreleased]


## [0.0.18] - 2019-08-23

### Changed
- Upgraded the "spencer-mortensen/exceptions" dependency


## [0.0.17] - 2019-07-07

### Changed
- The "Path::fromString($input)" methods now accept integer input.


## [0.0.16] - 2018-07-03

### Added
- You can now write the entire contents of a directory using the "Directory::write" method
  by passing in an associative array that maps a file or directory name to its contents.

### Changed
- Renamed: "SpencerMortensen\Filesystem\Paths\Path" => "SpencerMortensen\Filesystem\Path"
- Renamed: "WindowsPath::getDrive()" => "WindowsPath::getPrefix()"

### Removed
- Removed: "Filesystem::getPath()"
- Removed: "Filesystem::getDirectory($string)"
- Removed: "Filesystem::getFile($string)"
- Removed: "Filesystem::getCurrentDirectory()"
